Module org.postgresql.pljava

Interface PLJavaBasedLanguage.SRFTemplate

All Known Subinterfaces:
PLJavaBasedLanguage.SRFTemplate.Materialize, PLJavaBasedLanguage.SRFTemplate.ValuePerCall
Enclosing interface:
PLJavaBasedLanguage
public static interface PLJavaBasedLanguage.SRFTemplate
Superinterface for the result of a prepareSRF call on a PL/Java-based set-returning function.

An instance returned by prepareSRF must implement at least one of the member subinterfaces. If it implements more than one, it will need to override the negotiate method to select the behavior to be used at a given call site.

  • Method Details

    • negotiate

      int negotiate(List<Class<? extends PLJavaBasedLanguage.SRFTemplate>> allowed)
      Returns the index of a preferred subinterface of SRFTemplate among a list of those the caller supports.

      The list is ordered with a caller's more-preferred choices early.

      An implementation could simply return the first index of an allowed class C such that this instanceof C to use the caller's preferred method always, or could make a choice informed by characteristics of the template.

      Returns:
      the index within allowed of the interface to be used at this call site, or -1 if no interface in allowed is supported.
